CARBO CRYSTAL CC7 

Crystal Carbo blades are developed in close cooperation with Liu Guoliang, Xu Xin and other members of the Chinese National Team. Both the CC5 and CC7 have carbon layers inside, along with STIGA’s famous NCT and Crystal treatment on the surface. CC7 blade is a more powerful blade than the CC5. It is recommended for highly skilled attackers with excellent technique. The blade is outstanding when you are playing back off the table and getting into topspin rallies. With this blade you can feel the long trajectory in your topspin strokes and gain control over the game. If you like to play topspin against topspin, then this is the blade for you.
